'''Tiirarka Islaamka''' ({{lang-ar|أركان الإسلام}}; {{lang-en|Five Pillars of Islam}}; ''{{transl|ar|DIN|arkān al-Islām}}''; Sidoo kale ''{{transl|ar|DIN|arkān al-dīn}}'' {{lang|ar|أركان الدين}}) 
waa shanta tiir ee aasaaska u ah diinta [[Islaam]]ka, kuwaasi oo ah waajib (fardi) laga rabo ineey u hogaansanaadaan dhamaan dadka [[Muslim]]ka ah.<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/295625/Pillars-of-Islam Pillars of Islam, Encyclopædia Britannica] (en)</ref><ref>[http://www.oxfordislamicstudies.com/article/opr/t125/e1859?_hi=17&_pos= Pillars of Islam Oxford Centre for Islamic Studies, Oxford University, United Kingdom] (en)</ref><ref>[http://www.pbs.org/empires/islam/faithpillars.html Five Pillars, Public Broadcasting Service (PBS) United Kingdom] (en)</ref><ref>[http://people.ucalgary.ca/~elsegal/I_Transp/IO5_FivePillars.html The Five Pillars of Islam University of Calgary, Canada], (en)</ref>

Sida ku xusan [[xadiis]]ka iyo sunaha, shanta tiir ee Islaamku waa:

# '''[[Shahadah]]''': '''''Qiritaanka in Ilaahay maahine aanu Ilaah kale jirin''''', Muxamadna uu Rasuulkii Ilaahay yahay:- Waa albaabka uu qofku Islaamnimada kasoo galo, waana in qofku qalbiga ka rumeeyaa in Ilaahay mooyee aanu jirin Ilaah kale oo xaq lagu caabudaa carabkana uu ka yidhaahdo isaga oo dhahaya "اشهد ان لا اله الا الله و اشهد ان محمد رسول الله ""Ash-hadu Allaa Ilaaha Illallaahu Wa Ash-hadu Anna Muxamadun Rasuulu-Laah" .
# '''[[Salaad]]da''':- Waa tiirka laf dhabarka u ah diinta Islaamka waana shan Salaadood oo uu addoonku tukanayo habeenkii iyo maalintii, 
# '''[[Zaka]]da''':- Waa tiirka saddexaad,waxaana ay waajib ku tahay dadka hantida leh in ay in go'an oo ay diinta Islaamku u goysay ay Sako u bixiyaan si loo siiyo dadka ay ku baxdo, qofkii diidana dawladda [[Islaam]]ka ayaa xoog kaga qaadaysa si loo gaadhsiiya dadkii xaqa u lahaa, qofkii jiritaankeeda beeniyana diinta Islaamkaayuu kaga baxayaa. 
# '''[[Soon]]ka''':- Waa tiirka afraad, waana waajib saaran qof kasta oo [[Muslim]] ah, waana wajib ah in qofku ka soomanaado cuntada, cabitaanka iyo galmoodka laga bilaabo marka waagu dillaaco ilaa laga gaaraayo qoraxda marka ay dhacdo , qofkii jiritaankiisa beeniyana diinta Islaamka ayuu kaga baxayaa.
# '''[[Xaj]]ka''':- Waa tiirka shanaad,waxaana ay waajib ku tahay dadka kari kara ee hanti u haysta uu ku xajiyo,waana halmar inta uu nool yahay, isagoo addoonku tagaya Maka Almukarama si uu u soo guto Xajka isla markaana booqanaya Madiina , qofkii jiritaankeeda beeniyana diinta Islaamka ayuu kaga baxayaa.

